marketing.showcaseDescription:
Experience RSTechED 2012 in a whole new way

RSTechED 2012 has introduced a mobile app and desktop web portal for attendees to get even more from the event. Customize your experience before, during and after the show! You are able to plan your visit, tag favorites, manage your agenda, get directions, request appointments with other attendees, and much more.

Get started by selecting your preferred device below!

*The mobile website can be accessed on virtually all mobiles phones. Some features may be limited due to device browser limitations.

Simply visit http://visitors2.eventgenie.com/rsteched2012

visitorPortal.welcomeTop:
Experience RSTechED 2015 in a whole new way!


•  Browse schedules, speakers and sessions across 140+ sessions and labs, 740+ hours of training in five days!
•  Mark favorites so you don’t miss them and can reference them after the event
•  Network with other participants by exchanging messages and pre-arranging meetings
•  View hotel and event maps, important event information, meeting room locations, meal hours and locations
•  Find useful, relevant links and downloads
•  Join in the social media feeds and stay up on event news in one place
visitorPortal.loginHelp:
What's Inside?

By logging in you can:-

  • Plan your visit

  • Build your agenda

  • Engage with others

  • Synchronize it all with your Smartphone

If you have registered for the event, and are having trouble logging in, use the forgotten password link, and if the probelm persists, contact us.

Don't forget to get your Smartphone App!

visitorPortal.myProfileHelp:
Maximize your networking potential and make the right impression by updating your profile. Other attendees will be able to see it, and if you make appointments with exhibitors, they will too. To start networking with other people click the 'Find People' button above. After you've selected someone you can send them a message or a meeting request. Don't forget, you can continue networking on the move using your mobile app.

You can opt out of networking at any time by flicking the switch below to 'off', or doing the same on the mobile app. Your profile will instantly be removed from view.

visitorPortal.loginBottomLeft:
Privacy notice:

By logging into this service, your profile will become visible to other registered event attendees using the service. Your profile will contain your name, company, department and job title, and you may add a description and select interests. You may switch off your profile altogether if you prefer. Your other preferences will not be visible to anyone else. This service is provided by GenieMobile Ltd
